column5: Well at 4 AM tomorrow I am heading for the Timmins area for a little fishing   and relaxation. Hope to have a good report and lots of pictures for you when I get back on Friday night, that is if the bears don't get us  . Hope every one has a great week and manages to get on the water. See you soon.   Mike
Dress warm, I hear there's a winter storm warning up there right now.  Good luck!  Sinker
